                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>. Aged 32.—<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</hi>—</rs>
                  <hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18440205-522-punishment-1" type="punishmentDescription">
