                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-522-18440205 t18440205-522-punishment-1"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MALLER</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18440205-522-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
